column29: WITH SYSIBM.PROCEDURES    ( PROCEDURE_CAT,          PROCEDURE_SCHEM,        PROCEDURE_NAME,         NUM_INPUT_PARAMS,       NUM_OUTPUT_PARAMS,      NUM_RESULT_SETS,        REMARKS,                PROCEDURE_TYPE,         SPECIFIC_NAME   ) AS (    SELECT     CAST( NULL AS VARCHAR(128) ) as PROCEDURE_CAT,     CAST( RTRIM( ROUTINESCHEMA ) as VARCHAR(128) ) as PROCEDURE_SCHEM,     CAST( ROUTINENAME as VARCHAR(128) ) as PROCEDURE_NAME,     INTEGER( 0 ) as NUM_INPUT_PARAMS,     INTEGER( 0 ) as NUM_OUTPUT_PARAMS,     SMALLINT( RESULT_SETS ) as NUM_RESULT_SETS,     CAST( REMARKS as VARCHAR(254) ) as REMARKS,     SMALLINT( 1 ) as PROCEDURE_TYPE,     CAST( SPECIFICNAME as VARCHAR(128) ) as SPECIFIC_NAME      FROM SYSIBM.SYSROUTINES      WHERE ROUTINETYPE = 'P'  AND ROUTINENAME LIKE 'WLM_SET_CLIENT_INFO' ESCAPE '\' )  SELECT PROCEDURE_CAT, PROCEDURE_SCHEM, PROCEDURE_NAME, NUM_INPUT_PARAMS, NUM_OUTPUT_PARAMS, NUM_RESULT_SETS, REMARKS, PROCEDURE_TYPE      FROM SYSIBM.PROCEDURES WHERE PROCEDURE_NAME LIKE 'WLM_SET_CLIENT_INFO' ESCAPE '\' ORDER BY 1,2,3

SELECT SS_WHOLESALE_COST , SR_NET_LOSS FROM STORE_SALES INNER JOIN STORE_RETURNS ON SR_TICKET_NUMBER = SS_TICKET_NUMBER AND SR_ITEM_SK = SS_ITEM_SK WHERE SS_STORE_SK = 2 AND SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK = 2451680
